release_body:
This is a major new version of the Python client library for SignalFx.

The client library is now structured as three API sub-clients:
* the ingest client;
* the REST metadata API client;
* the SignalFlow API client.

The major new feature available in this new version is the availability of the SignalFlow real-time streaming analytics API. For more information, see the [README](https://github.com/signalfx/signalfx-python/blob/master/README.rst) and the [Developers documentation](https://developers.signalfx.com).
